e content\n\n## Pending\n- Save X001 to `rag/drafts/x001_final.md`\n- Start NurseSphere article writing process\n\n## X001 Tiny's Tweaked Version (11:50 SAST) — SAVED\n\n**File:** `rag/drafts/x001_final.md`\n\n**What Tiny changed (NavaSM training observations):**\n\nTweet 1:\n- My version: \"Spread your agency's 30% fee over 12 weeks\"\n- Tiny's: \"Spread the recruitment agency fee over 12 weeks\" (no \"your agency\" — clearer ownership)\n- Added: 😃🤝 emojis at end, 𝘤𝘶𝘭𝘵𝘂𝘳𝘢𝘭 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗼𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝗮𝗹 𝗳𝗶𝘁 (bold specific fit criteria, not just \"fit\")\n- Added: \"for hiring healthcare facilities\" (context clarification)\n\nTweet 2:\n- \"No, wait... Hold on, nice dream🤡\" — replaced my plain \"Nice dream\" with this stronger opener\n- 🤡 = clown emoji — mockery of the hypothetical, not just dismissal\n- Added: \"while taking on extra risk\" (deepens the dismantle)\n- Added: 💰💵🤑 (cash/emotion — agency's motivation)\n- Added: admin/HR question as second dismantling point (additional real-world friction)\n- Note: Tiny kept BOTH dismantle arguments (agency cash flow + admin), I dropped admin in v3\n\nTweet 3:\n- \"𝗭𝗲𝗿𝗼 𝘂𝗽𝗳𝗿𝗼𝗻𝘁 𝗳𝗲𝗲𝘀!\" — bold ALL CAPS framing, stronger than my version\n- Added: 🤝 🎯 at end (collaboration + precision)\n- \"hire proves they belong\" — better than \"proves themselves\" (belonging = cultural fit signal)\n- Kept CTA at end\n\n**Key NavaSM learnings:**\n1. Bold specific criteria (cultural AND operational fit, not generic \"fit\")\n2. 🤡 for mockery, not just dismissal\n3. 💰💵🤑 = cash triple for agency motivation\n4. ALL CAPS + bold for emphasis on key differentiators\n5. Second dismantle point (admin) adds real-world friction\n6. \"Hold on, nice dream🤡\" > \"Nice dream. But impractical.\"\n7. \"proves they belong\" > \"proves themselves\" (belonging = LTC cultural fit language)\n\n**Status:** ✅ Final. Saved to `rag/drafts/x001_final.md`\n\n### 09:50 UTC (11:50 SAST)\n- Sprint check-in fires — TUI session (agent:main:tui-993acfe0-532b...) active at 11:41 SAST\n- X001 final: ✅ SAVED to `rag/drafts/x001_final.md` (1448 bytes, Tiny's version with \"hire\" → \"hiring\" edit)\n- TUI last message: Tiny working X001 final polish, \"Hiring\" vs \"hiring\" word choice resolved\n- X001 status: ✅ COMPLETE — next = NurseSphere article (Post 002)\n- Nava RAG: COMPLETE (>48h — excluded per rule)\n- Sprint: X001 ✅ → NurseSphere article IN PROGRESS in TUI → Post 002 concept → writing lesson → cloud backup (17:00 SAST)\n- Main session: heartbeat-only, Tiny working in TUI\n\n### 09:51 UTC (11:51 SAST) — TUI Session Active\n- Tiny reviewing X Post 001 revision (Mar 22 draft)\n- Feedback provided:\n  1. Change \"recruiting healthcare facilities\" → \"hiring healthcare facilities\"\n  2. Still reads as THREE tweets — second starts \"No, wait...\", third starts \"We solved it differently...\"\n- TUI assistant revised with \"hiring\" change, kept three-tweet structure\n- Tiny's concern (three tweets = fragmented) not yet addressed — needs re-edit\n- No new instructions issued yet\n\n### 10:20 UTC (12:20 SAST)\n- TUI session (46e65f89) active ~12:12 UTC (8 min ago) — Tiny working on X thread/browser work\n- TUI last state: assistant asked for Custom GPT URL or Chrome relay screenshot\n- Tiny's concern (three tweets fragmented) still unaddressed in TUI draft\n- Main session not directly messaged by Tiny\n- Nava RAG: COMPLETE (Mar 17, >48h — excluded per rule)\n- Sprint pending: X thread review (in TUI), Post 002 NurseSphere, writing lesson\n\n## NavaAA Architecture Confirmed (12:11 SAST)\n\n**Three-way system:**\n- You (Tiny) — ultimate authority, writes final drafts\n- Me (Dawn) — Tiny's digital twin. Knows Tiny's voice, finds gaps, accesses Gemini for deep research, evaluates NavaAA output, suggests changes\n- NavaAA — executes drafts per Dawn's direction, proposes H2s/H3s, iterates on feedback\n\n**Dawn's specific jobs during article creation:**\n1. Tell NavaAA what to write (topic/gap identified)\n2. Query Gemini for deep research to feed Na